        ],
        "recommendations": [
          "We recommend scheduling a brief operational review with Plano to audit current scheduling templates and patient flow patterns. Given Plano's 30.8-minute average delay sits 68% above company benchmarks despite strong scheduler compliance of 85.0%, the issue likely stems from appointment density or buffer-time assumptions rather than scheduling discipline\u2014a targeted review of appointment spacing and chair-to-nurse assignments could unlock meaningful gains without adding resources."
